EventPayload<Integer> baz = new EventPayload<>(12).     produceIntegerPayload.sendBody(baz).     produceFooQualifier.sendBody(456L).     produceBarQualifier.sendBody(495L).     produceObject.sendBody(777L).     assertThat(observer.getObjectEvents(), contains("string", foo, 1234, "test", bar, baz, 456L, 495L, 777L)).     assertThat(observer.getStringEvents(), contains("string", "test")).     assertThat(observer.getStringPayloadEvents(), contains(foo)).     assertThat(observer.getIntegerPayloadEvents(), contains(bar, baz)).     assertThat(observer.getDefaultQualifierEvents(), contains("string", foo, 1234, "test", bar, baz, 777L)).     assertThat(observer.getFooQualifierEvents(), contains(456L)).     assertThat(observer.getBarQualifierEvents(), contains(495L)). }
